, and Committees'; the role of think tanks, NGOs, and political parties; and the developments provided by university teaching and research. Analysing the conceptual frameworks and methodologies used from a meta-theoretical perspective, it provides a panoramic picture of the perspectives and challenges of policy analysis in Argentina.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aPolitical planningzArgentina. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / General.2bisacsh1 aAgoff, Sergio L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlutman, Gustavo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBulcourf, Pablo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBulcourf, Pablo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCampos Ríos, Maximiliano, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCao, Horacio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCardozo, Nelson, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCardozo, Nelson, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCiolli, Vanesa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aConrero, Sofía, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCrudo, Silvio A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCurti, Guillermina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDarmohraj, Adrián, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDiéguez, Gonzalo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDíaz, Cristina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEstévez, Alejandro M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFerrari, Paola, econtri